    • Constructor Detail

      • Answer

        public Answer(java.lang.String checked,
      java.lang.String answer,
      java.lang.String removed)
        Each answer the user types is represented by an Object of type Answer. The user can modify the text and choose whether this answer is the correct one or not.
        Parameters:
        checked - The property of the answer: it might be marked as correct (✔) or incorrect (✘).
        answer - The text of the answer that the user can enter.
        removed - The String value of the hyphen minus symbol (-) the button to remove this particular answer has.
